{
  "text": "Vascular relaxation in response to \u00b5M concentrations of oestrogen is not different in wild-type mice compared with mice lacking a functional ER\u03b1 indicating that ER\u03b2 might be responsible [CITATION_1] . The aim of the present study was to investigate the importance of ER\u03b2 for relaxation caused by pharmacological concentrations of oestrogen by using arterial preparations from mice lacking functional ER\u03b2.",
